{{#exhibits}}
<w:p>
  <w:r>
    <w:t><w:b>Overage Charges for {{exhibitCombinationName}}:</w:b> {{exhibitOveragePerUser}} per User | {{exhibitOveragePerServer}} per server per month</w:t>
  </w:r>
  {{#exhibitOveragePerGB}}
  <w:r>
    <w:t> | {{exhibitOveragePerGB}} per GB</w:t>
  </w:r>
  {{/exhibitOveragePerGB}}
</w:p>
{{/exhibits}}

<!-- 
STRUCTURE BREAKDOWN:
1. {{#exhibits}} - Starts loop for each exhibit
2. <w:p> - Opens paragraph
3. <w:r> - Opens text run
4. <w:t> - Text content with combination name and per-user/per-server costs
5. </w:r> - Closes first text run (ONLY ONE CLOSING TAG NEEDED HERE)
6. {{#exhibitOveragePerGB}} - Conditional: only if per-GB exists
7. <w:r> - Opens new text run for per-GB
8. <w:t> - Per-GB text
9. </w:r> - Closes per-GB text run
10. {{/exhibitOveragePerGB}} - Closes conditional (NOTE: Capital 'O' in Overage)
11. </w:p> - Closes paragraph
12. {{/exhibits}} - Closes loop

IMPORTANT: 
- Remove any duplicate </w:r> tags
- Use {{/exhibitOveragePerGB}} (capital O), not {{/exhibitoveragePerGB}}
-->

